File path

/

/Work 

/Work/report.doc

/Work/Project

/Work/Project/talk.ppt

Absoulte file path
-. /Users/Work/Project/talk.ppt

Relative file path
-. Working directory
-. ./talk.ppt

-. . means the current working directory
-. Going upwards in the current directory
-. ../report.doc
-. ../../Work/report.doc # write dot dot twice if you want to go up twice in a file path
